				<td colspan="2"><span>Just got this today (woot, finally after about 15 Wise kills <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> ), and was wondering if there was a way to include this in a hotkey, along with a /stopsong before it. I'm used to the 11 22 33 44 form of twisting, but with this I have to do 11 22 33 34. Is there a way to activate this from a hotkey so I would be able to still use 11 22 33 44?</span></td>
